      "title": "Govt. approves 5-year multiple entry VISA for tourists from 35 nations with 6 months stay",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government has approved a five-year multiple entry tourist visa with six months stay for visitors from 35 countries, Tourism Minister Harin Fernando said.",
        "He said that the decision was taken to help boost repeat tourism in the country.",
        "In addition to the one year multiple entry and single entry tourists visas which have six months stay period, which was earlier limited 30 days. (Chatuanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
